{
  "texts": [
    "• The mode (3,3) is also highly reliable, with a mean of MM% = 1.0 ± 2.0.",
    "We note, however, that the largest mismatches occur for equal-mass systems q ∼ 1, for which this mode is suppressed by symmetry.",
    "This suggests that the higher values of the mismatch in such simulations is guided by numerical uncertainties.",
    "• The mode (2, 1) has mismatches comparable with those of the mode (3, 3), MM% = 2.0 ± 9.0, except for a subset of simulations in which the accuracy drops.",
    "These simulations lie in a region of the parameter space in which this mode is not suppressed."
  ]
}